graph TB
    subgraph "ODH Notebook Controller"
        OpenshiftReconciler[OpenshiftNotebookReconciler<br/>Main Controller]
        NotebookWebhook[NotebookWebhook<br/>Mutating Webhook]
        OAuthManager[OAuth Proxy Manager]
        RouteManager[Route Manager]
        NetworkPolicyMgr[Network Policy Manager]
        CertManager[Certificate Manager]

        OpenshiftReconciler -->|manages| OAuthManager
        OpenshiftReconciler -->|manages| RouteManager
        OpenshiftReconciler -->|manages| NetworkPolicyMgr
        OpenshiftReconciler -->|manages| CertManager
    end

    User[User/Dashboard] -->|creates| NotebookCR[Notebook CR<br/>kubeflow.org/v1]
    NotebookCR -->|intercepted by| NotebookWebhook
    NotebookWebhook -->|injects OAuth sidecar| NotebookCR
    NotebookCR -->|watched by| OpenshiftReconciler

    subgraph "Created Resources (Non-OAuth)"
        Route1[OpenShift Route<br/>Edge TLS]
        Service1[ClusterIP Service<br/>8888/TCP]
        NetPol1[NetworkPolicy]
    end

    subgraph "Created Resources (OAuth Mode)"
        Route2[OpenShift Route<br/>Reencrypt TLS]
        Service2[ClusterIP Service<br/>8443/TCP TLS]
        ServiceAccount[ServiceAccount]
        OAuthSecret[OAuth Config Secret]
        TLSSecret[TLS Certificate Secret]
        NetPol2[NetworkPolicy]
    end

    RouteManager -->|creates| Route1
    RouteManager -->|creates| Route2
    OAuthManager -->|creates| Service2
    OAuthManager -->|creates| ServiceAccount
    OAuthManager -->|creates| OAuthSecret
    CertManager -->|creates| TLSSecret
    NetworkPolicyMgr -->|creates| NetPol1
    NetworkPolicyMgr -->|creates| NetPol2

    subgraph "External Dependencies"
        KubeflowController[Kubeflow Notebook Controller]
        OpenShiftRouter[OpenShift Ingress Controller]
        OAuthServer[OpenShift OAuth Server]
        ServiceCA[Service CA Operator]
    end

    OpenshiftReconciler -->|coordinates with| KubeflowController
    Route1 -->|consumed by| OpenShiftRouter
    Route2 -->|consumed by| OpenShiftRouter
    OAuthManager -->|integrates| OAuthServer
    CertManager -->|uses| ServiceCA

    subgraph "Internal ODH Integrations"
        Dashboard[ODH Dashboard]
        TrustedCABundle[Trusted CA Bundle ConfigMap]
    end

    Route1 -.->|linked in UI| Dashboard
    Route2 -.->|linked in UI| Dashboard
    CertManager -->|mounts| TrustedCABundle

    style OpenshiftReconciler fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookWebhook fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style OAuthManager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style RouteManager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NetworkPolicyMgr fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style CertManager fill:#4a90e2,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style NotebookCR fill:#f5a623,stroke:#333,stroke-width:2px
    style KubeflowController fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OpenShiftRouter fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style OAuthServer fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style ServiceCA fill:#999,stroke:#333
    style Dashboard fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
    style TrustedCABundle fill:#7ed321,stroke:#333
